## 4.1 MVP Goal
Deliver the minimum version that proves the product promise:

> Define tables, generate data, expose working REST endpoints, and use them in development immediately.

## 4.2 MVP Features
The MVP should include:

- user authentication
- project creation
- table creation
- field creation and editing
- field types and simple constraints
