# 12. Metadata Database Schema Design

Below is the conceptual relational structure for the metadata database.

## 12.1 Tables
- users
- projects
- project_tables
- table_fields
- relationships
- endpoints
- environments
- seed_jobs

## 12.2 Relationship Overview
- one user has many projects
- one project has many tables
- one table has many fields
- one project has many relationships
- one project has many endpoints
- one project has one or more environments
- one project has many seed jobs

