# 24. Risks and Non-Goals

## 24.1 Main Risks
- overbuilding the canvas before core backend generation works
- mixing metadata and runtime records
- trying to support too many field types too early
- attempting full Supabase export in v1
- allowing unrestricted custom endpoints too early
- turning the tool into a generic BaaS too soon

## 24.2 Non-Goals for Now
- replace Supabase
- replace Postman
- replace a production backend
- support every API pattern
- support every SQL feature

